node.text:
There’s many different approaches when discussing this topic and believe me, there’s no right or wrong. It all depends on the mission and the goal and of course the experience on every individual 💯. 

*This excerpt is from my latest youtube video // from my trip to Miami for the Power House conference. Full video is about 25 min, so when you get a chance, pop it open, sit back and enjoy 💪🏾

#LVFT #livefit #graphicdesigner #creativeartist

node.text:
Official trailer finally leaked out! I guess appearing in a movie can be ✅ off my bucket list!🙏 Thanks to director and star actor @chrissoriano for casting me as a Muay Thai fighter from the streets of LA 😎. This was such a fun experience, working and getting to know some awesome peeps. You can catch a little snippet of my spin kick in the trailer haha 😅. 

Movie premieres in August! 

Also, shout out to executive producer @mannypacquiao 🥊! 

Thank you! 🙏

First of all I’m no guitarist... I’m a drummer that’s been around a ton of guitar players and taught myself 🤷🏽‍♂️😅. Got bored with this quarantine shit so I decided to mess around. Anyways, made this whole riff up in just a few minutes haha, taking little breaks to ease my mind. Recorded this on the iPhone, had @ryan_lvft just film and then I edited everything on final cut cuz I’m too lazy to re-install logic and get other apps. I recorded a few different times just to get the second guitar and double bass to come out. Anyways, enjoy! Who plays an instruments!? Send me some guitar riffs or something and I’ll drum over it!!! Haha 
#LVFT #breakdown #riffs #hardcore #chugchug

Thank you guys for tuning in, I’ve been MIA with the entrepreneurial side of things solely because I actually have businesses to run 😂🤷🏽‍♂️. But I’ve been asked constantly about how I’m dealing with the statewide “stay at home” issue and what people should be doing. First of all, I’m no expert on these things, I’m just sharing my personal views and opinions as a CEO, designer and business owner.

A lot of these things, companies should already be doing, but now since we are all at home with plenty of down time, we should look a little deeper into each subject.

Here are a few tips I shared within this video for pretty much everyone that has a brand, a personal brand, a company and or business; doesn’t matter if it’s an e-commerce based business or a service business: - PERSONAL LEVEL COMMUNICATION WITH YOUR CUSTOMERS. *Constructive criticism. - PATCH BLEEDING HOLES *Analyze and regroup.
- RE-BRANDING *Website Facelift. *New Marketing Campaign Ideas. *New color schemes. *Possible new logos and categories. -DO NOT PAY ATTENTION TO YOUR COMPETITION. *Focus on what you’re good at and know 😉. Thanks again for watching. Drop a comment, share this and start hammering these out!! 😬🔥💻📊📈

node.text:
This Saturday the official LIVE FIT. Bootcamp will be held here at the LVFT. HQ Hosted by myself @randall_pich and head trainer @thomasj_usa . Link is in bio for more details and admission. 
Why a bootcamp? Well live fit apparel would of never existed if it wasn’t for my prior career in personal training. With that being said, LVFT always had deep roots in the field of exercise and kinesiology. With 8 years of extensive experience training clients of all ages, running bootcamps and small group training I decided to get back to his roots and open the doors back up and focus on building with the local community again. This time around I’ll have Thomas alongside, a pro MMA fighter and experienced personal trainer, training and running the bootcamp as well. 
So if you haven’t, head to the link, grab a ticket and come prepared Saturday morning! And yes, you know the whole group will get a ton of LVFT goodies and afterwards we’ll enjoy some desserts provided by @paderiabakehouse 🤘🏽😁. Let’s go!

node.text:
Saturday October 19th! 
The LVFT x WESTCA fashion show is around the corner! All of you in southern Cali who couldn’t make it the last few years cuz it was in San Jose, well this year we are going to host it HERE at the LVFT HQ Huntington Beach! Toxic Beach House Bikinis will also be joining us!! So we’ll have a total of 3 brands showcasing their latest and exclusive collections!! There will be food, cocktails and GIFT BAGS for every attendee! 
SPOTS ARE LIMITED, for more info click on the link on the  @live_fit_apparel IG 👊🏼👊🏼 HOPE TO SEE YOU GUYS THERE!!

node.text:
I’ve traveled the world and have been to a handful of countries, everywhere I go people say, “You’re from Cali or America huh.” Or “American right?” 

Without me even saying anything lol. 

And then when I travel outside of SoCal people say, “You from LA or OC huh.” Whether it be NorCal to Vegas, to OKC, to New York all the way down to Florida. 

What gives it away?😅🤷🏾‍♂️ 

What do you guys think? 

*Here’s a little set from today 😎 Releasing some NEW @live_fit_apparel raglan tees this Friday plus restocking some as well. 🤙🏽

Anyways I wanna hear you’re guys answers, I’m genuinely curious lol.

node.text:
So I’ve been somewhat MIA for the past few days… Here’s what I was doing.

On the surface, yea it looks like fun tactical training… and yes it was fun and it was somewhat tactical but I was actually at the FTX 002 Extreme Ownership training at @echelonfront learning leadership skills and principles w/ real SEALs. And man did it change the way I look at EVERYTHING. And y’all know me, I don’t bullshit💯 

Thank you @jpdinnell for this 🙏 If it wasn’t for you I don’t think I may have ever switched that light bulb 💡 within my mindset. 

This literally was a game changer // LIFE changer 💯

*They were kind enough to let us film bits and pieces and I can’t wait to share that with you all too. 🙏

#ECHELONFRONT #LVFT #leadership #extremeownership #LIVEFIT

node.text:
Found this nomad they call @maria_g_fit wandering around the city and decided to interview her!😂

So good catching up with our athlete Maria, so many good things had happened and IS happening since the pandemic and since she decided to travel the world. 

Just got done filming a short but powerful interview with her here at the @live_fit_apparel HQ. Can’t wait til it’s all done so we can share it with you guys. Anyways, peep the magazine cover 👀🙏.

#PROUD #LVFT #livefit #livefitapparel #fitness #fitlife #livefitathlete #motivation

When the pump gets real // the layers start coming off💪🏾. 

I don’t even need to ask, I know you guys do this too🙋🏽‍♂️😅 .

Anyways here’s a sneak peek of another short sleeve heavyweight sweater but now a crewneck instead of hoodie. Also the new @live_fit_apparel ultra soft TEAM USA tank🇺🇸.

Alight, back to the grind! Peace ✌️ 

#LVFT #livefit #livefitapparel #outfits #gymfits #gymoutfits
